ex' is 'part of' some 'occipital lobe'\",\n  \"comments\": [],\n  \"title\": \"[Text Def] UBERON:0022232 secondary visual cortex has no textual definition\",\n  \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3471\"\n}","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778596654921,"end":1778596654931}},"id":"prt_e1c9f2501001eIjwDYhBG1q2A2","sessionID":"ses_1e3615130ffeikDHJ0VFv1PYWC","messageID":"msg_e1c9eaf96001jexacz0idjhN0A"}}
